## 💡 Key Insights

- Customer purchasing trends can be identified through interactive visualizations.
- Product category performance helps businesses understand customer demand.
- Customer demographics reveal purchasing patterns across different groups.
- Payment method analysis highlights customer preferences.

---

## 📈 Business Recommendations

- Maintain sufficient inventory for high-demand product categories.
- Design targeted marketing campaigns based on customer demographics.
- Improve customer experience by supporting preferred payment methods.
- Use dashboard insights for strategic business decisions.

